This is a minimal version of zkfarmer for Isilon file servers.

* Installation of the zookeeper CLI
tar xvfz zk-c.tar.gz
cd c
./configure --build=amd64-unknown-kfreebsd-gnu --prefix=/usr/local
make
make install

# Usage of zkjoiner.py
The environment variable ZKHOST must contain the ip:port of the zookeeper cluster.
The script zkjoiner.py takes only one argument: the name of the farm to join.
